   "len": 35,
   "en": "\"Others call me...something @else.\"",
   "zh": "「也有人叫我……@else（別）的稱呼。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 275,
   "len": 17,
   "en": "She winks at you.",
   "zh": "她向汝眨了眨眼。",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 315,
   "len": 39,
   "en": "\"Perhaps some time I will @show you...\"",
   "zh": "「也許哪天我會@show（讓汝）見識一番……」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 355,
   "len": 27,
   "en": "\"I think you get the idea.\"",
   "zh": "「汝應當意會。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 394,
   "len": 11,
   "en": "\"Not here.\"",
   "zh": "「此處不便。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 415,
   "len": 38,
   "en": "\"I raise horses here, in the stables.\"",
   "zh": "「我在此馬廄養育駿馬。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 456,
   "len": 47,
   "en": "\"I also sell @horses, if you wish to @buy one.\"",
   "zh": "「若有意@horses（購買），在下亦@buy（買）馬匹。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 519,
   "len": 65,
   "en": "\"I can hardly bear to part with any of these magnificent beasts.\"",
   "zh": "「吾實難捨這些神駿離去。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 587,
   "len": 45,
   "en": "\"But there are a few that fail to please me.\"",
   "zh": "「然有幾匹令我稍感不滿。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 635,
   "len": 53,
   "en": "\"If you wish to @buy one of them, just say the word.\"",
   "zh": "「若有意@buy（買）其中一匹，言聲便是。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 705,
   "len": 32,
   "en": "\"Come to my shop when I'm open!\"",
   "zh": "「開店時歡迎光臨！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 754,
   "len": 23,
   "en": "\"Come back again soon!\"",
   "zh": "「快快再來！」",
   "note": ""
  },
